Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Header,,0,0,0,,This is a Gentlemen of the Han free fansub.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Zhuge Liang set Bowang Slope on fire at the start of his career
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:13.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and bruised the morale of the Cao army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:18.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Not resigned to failure, Cao Cao ordered Cao Ren to attack Xinye again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.10,Thinking,NTP,0,0,0,,Little did he knew, that he was falling into Zhuge Liang's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:28.45,Thinking,NTP,0,0,0,,Cao Ren was fortunate enough to make a narrow escape in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:39.88,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,3500,3800)\pos(1146.263,694.356)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That Zhuge peasant! How dare he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare my armies, we will exterminate Xinye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,00,550,5600,6000)\pos(1083.67,704.545)}Liú Yè \N Styled: Ziyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor intents to take Jīng-Xiāng for its masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So this time, when we enter Xiāngyang, \Nwe must conquer the hearts of the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei has already led the people into Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not summon him to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If Liu Bei refuses, \Nthen the people may see our 'mercy'...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he accepts, then the lands of\NJīng-Province are settled without struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan can work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who can be the envoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Chancellor, there is one man among our army very close with Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He can be our advocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is so close with Liu Bei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,None other than Xu Shu—Xu Yuanzhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He has not offered a single thought to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If we send him away, he will not return!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor does not need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Yuanzhi always cared about his reputation. If he doesn't return, he would be ridiculed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not he is successful, he will definitely return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then. Order Xu Yuanzhi to set out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.44,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(232.557,735.303)}Xu Shu\NStyled: Yuanzhi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,—Yuanzhi to be sent from the heavens, just like the sweet rain after a long drought!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am delighted from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mister Shuijing has predicted long ago—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,— that if you have the Sleeping Dragon, the world is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that it is indeed true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since our last meeting at my hut, you have made me busy day and night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, has Cao Cao let you come to persuade my Lord to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao has sent me to persuade you,\N so that he can win the people's hearts this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Cao Cao has his armies traveling along eight routes —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,, — and intends to enter by damming the Bai-River. I'm afraid Fancheng won't hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You must make another plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:30.38,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,100,550,4600,5000)\pos(202.83,744.22)}Zhuge Liang\NStyled: \NKongming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat is the first choice of the Thirty-Six Stratagems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I am able to meet you all today, my wish is fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With two armies fighting, it is wrong to overstay. I will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have come, you must not return to that damned place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, if I don't return, I would be mocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother has passed, and I will carry the pain until my last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, even though I am situated in the Cao camp—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,—I swore to never in my life form a plan or stratagem for Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the Sleeping Dragon's help—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,—what fear could you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.93,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,50,2500,3000)\pos(1137.443,720.659)}Liu Bei\NStyled: Xuande
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone–farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you must abandon Fancheng at once\N and retreat to Xiangyang for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Xinye and Fancheng have been with me so long—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,— how can I part with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Lord, if you take them with you, they will only be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:26.36,Style Names,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,4500,5000)\pos(220.443,659.75)}Sun Qian\NStyled: Gongyou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why not let them run for themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All great accomplishers of old —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,— regarded the common men as the foundation and to be of utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruler is worth less than the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Lord, you can order someone to tell the people—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—that they can choose to follow us,\N or to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be as Strategos says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Attention, all ye people! \NThe Cao army is coming to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Those who wish to follow Lord Liu  —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- We follow with Lord Liu, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:12.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,, — must cross the river for refuge in Xiangyang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Cross the river for refuge in Xiangyang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Attention, all ye people,\N the Cao army is coming to attack!
