Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.32,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,522)}Xiangyang
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear nephew Liu Cong, please open the city gates quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We are only here to save the people, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, open the city gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear nephew Liu Cong, quickly open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.76,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351.989,678.992)}Liu Cong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The people are too tired and cannot go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear nephew Liu Cong, please open the gates quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need to keep the people, my troops will leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur11.208} Lies! Those words cannot be trusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:49.12,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5000,5500)\pos(1002.125,651.902)}Cai Mao\NStyled: Degui
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Liu Bei is sending his army to denounce us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's using the commoners as a cover! You mustn't fall for this trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Greet him with arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't harm the innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent or not, all is uncertain—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,—but if we let them in, it'll bring chaos to Xiangyang again. Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitorous bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu is a man of virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.52,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)\pos(1079.67,701.083)}Wèi Yán\NStyled: Wéncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has come to save the people, \Nwhy are you keeping them from the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Imperial Uncle Liu, lead your troops in to kill the wicked traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei Yan! How dare you rebel! Do you recognize me as Senior General Wen Pin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wen Pin!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect the people, but now I'm endangering them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't enter Xiangyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, abandon Xiangyang at once and turn to Jiangling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiangling is an important location in Jing-Province. Why not rest there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wen Pin! I will spare your life today— we will meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wei Yan, don't you flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:49.73,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(272.443,462.598)\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)}Wen Pin\NStyled: Zhongye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:06.68,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)\pos(302.443,462.598)}Grave of Liu Biao,\NOverseer of Jing-Province
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have failed to live up to your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The sin is with me alone, \Nnot with the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that your spirit in heaven will rescue the people of Jing-Xiang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao's army has occupied Fancheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're preparing boats and rafts and will soon cross the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We are leading tens of thousands of people and can only travel about 10 {\i1}li{\i0} per day
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With such speed, when can we reach Jiangling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If the Cao army catches up, how can we resist them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't we temporarily abandon the people and advance ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, accomplishers of great deeds must have the people as their priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now that the people have joined me, \Nhow can I abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, the army will soon be upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can send Yunchang and Gongyou —
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,— towards Jiangxia to ask Liu Qi for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to raise his army and embark to meet us at Jiangling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yunchang, follow his orders and hurry to Jiangxia with Gongyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.80,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)\pos(1000.239,704.598)}Xún Yōu\NStyled: Gōngdá
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How many troops, horses, money, and grain are there in Jing-Province?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor, there are 50,000 cavalry —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, — 150,000 infantry, and 80,000 naval infantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the money and grain are at Jiangling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With the supplies from other places, there are enough —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, — to supply Chancellor Cao's victorious army for one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How many warships are there? Who was in command?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are 7000 warships of all sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zhang Yun and I were the commanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jing-Province has 280,000 troops and cavalry, 7,000 warships—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,—and the money and grain altogether are just about enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to support my army for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With the strength of such resources—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,—why did you generals surrender without a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How can the troops of Jing-Province dare to resist Chancellor's mighty army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intellect is unmatched in the world, you use the army like a god—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,—you are invincible! \NMy Chancellor, you are, of this age ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I grant you the title of \N{\i1}Marquis-Guardian of the South{\i0}—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,— and Grand Admiral of the naval force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang Yun is {\i1}Pacifying-Marquis{\i0} and {\i1}Vice-admiral of the naval force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep the naval force ready, and await for command.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,, Liu Cong, I have already granted you to be the Overseer of Qīng-Province —
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you weeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(157.102,401.462)\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)}Lady Cai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When we surrendered the city, you promised my son will be the Lord of Jing-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you sending us, mother and son, off to Qīng-Province?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The battles in Jing-Province are far from over, Liu Bei and Liu Qi refuse to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I appointed Liu Cong as the lord of Jing-Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,how could he keep his lands under his control?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is so, I do not wish to become an official!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to guard my parents' native lands. \NPlease allow me to become a commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Qīng-Province is near the capital. You can become an official under the imperial court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You avoid being harmed in Jing-Xiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I did this with you both in mind. Set out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lead fifty soldiers to Lady Cai, Liu Cong, and his party before they reach Qīng-Province —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Cai Mao and Zhang Yun are lesser men who can only flatter and slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They are of reprobate nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why were they granted such high ranks and entrusted with the naval force?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could not tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because we men of the north are inexperienced with naval warfare —
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,— so I must use those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After they have fulfill their purpose, \NI have other ways to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All the officers of Xiangyang are here already—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,—what made you alone take such time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As an official, I failed to protect my Lord's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is ashamed. What face do I have to see anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an official of integrity, rarely seen in Jing-Xiang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame that you haven't met a worthy master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wen Pin, I appoint you {\i1}Marquis of the Inner Pass{\i0}, and {\i1}Administrator of Jiangxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Liu Bei's party is traveling only 10{\i1} li {\i0}a day heading towards Jiangling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Jiangling a place of import in Jing-Xiang. It is rich in money and grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Liu Bei guards Jiangling, it would be very hard to dislodge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wen Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead your troops towards Jiangling and open up a way for our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Xu Chu, Zhang He!    - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang Liao, Li Dian! Yue Jin!     - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose 5,000 cavalry to advance day and night to catch up to Liu Bei!      - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiahou En!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I order you as the sword-bearer to carry {\i1}the Blue Pommel{\i0} and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We are traveling too slowly, what if the Cao army pursues us? How can we resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yunchang and Gongyou departed for Jiangxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have received no news, I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Liu Qi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I will need to trouble you to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved Liu Qi's life once. If he sees you, things will be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go there, but what of things here, Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.32,0:23:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, with Yide and Zilong, nothing will happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead 500 troops to escort the Strategos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Xianhe and Zizhong will protect my Lord here well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest assured, Strategos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the border with Dangyang county, and that hill is Jingshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass on the orders, we'll station on Jingshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, we should not station here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.85,0:24:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao now has Xiangyang and will definitely send troops after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are moving so slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If we stop, I fear that Cao Cao's troops will catch up before daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.12,0:24:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The people and soldiers are tired. How can we keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.59,0:24:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If we go on like this and the Cao army comes—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.98,0:24:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—we will not only fail to protect the people from them, but you will also be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.64,0:24:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord should leave the people and ride quickly to Jiangling!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.21,0:24:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, when the Cao army comes, disaster will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.91,0:25:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}The people have followed me all the way here from Xinye—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.91,0:25:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}—and have gone through many hardships
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.91,0:25:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}How can I abandon them without regard?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.61,0:25:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}Although the situation now is pressing—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.61,0:25:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}—I have sworn to share life and death with my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.11,0:25:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}We will live and perish together!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.61,0:25:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}Don't try to persuade me. Pass on my orders again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.61,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}We will station on Jingshan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.61,0:25:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303} Let the people get a night's worth of rest. We'll be on our way in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}Zilong will protect my family \Nand Yide will be our rearguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.71,0:25:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}Let's go, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.25,0:25:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.14,0:26:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, let me carry him for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cao army is coming! Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.17,0:26:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cao army is coming! Run for your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, elder brother, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.79,0:27:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cao army is coming from the northwest, run to the east at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.14,0:27:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.37,0:27:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry and follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.68,0:27:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu! Don't you run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wen Pin! How has Brother Jingsheng ever mistreated you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.02,0:27:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare betray your own lord for glory?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.14,0:27:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Submitting to Cao Cao, now killing your late master's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.29,0:27:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your conscience? Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.16,0:27:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Treacherous villain, Zhang Yide from Yan is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.60,0:28:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move. Try not to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.74,0:28:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The common people, old and young—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.29,0:28:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—Zilong, Mi Zizhong, Mi Zifang, and Jian Xianhe—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.10,0:28:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—where are they all?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.96,0:28:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, the Cao army had encircled all the commoners —
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,, — and massacred more than half. \NWe don't know where the others have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.11,0:29:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred thousand living souls all suffered because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.99,0:29:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the whereabouts of the people, of families, or the officers is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.40,0:29:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if one has a heart of stone and mind of iron, how can one not grieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.65,0:30:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.87,0:30:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.45,0:30:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.12,0:30:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to die, what reason do we have to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.80,0:30:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, General Mi is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.77,0:30:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,, My Lord, emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.01,0:30:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhao Zilong has defected to Cao Cao!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.81,0:30:31.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,200,5100,2000)\pos(1205,731.902)}Mi Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.94,0:30:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak no nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.68,0:30:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong is an old friend, how could he leave me for Cao Cao?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.59,0:30:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have seen how weak our forces were, \Nso he followed Cao Cao for the riches and honors
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.29,0:30:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.43,0:30:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zilong joined me when I was in misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,His heart is of iron and stone,\Nno riches and honors can move him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him ride towards the northwest with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will seek him later. If I run into him, I shall kill him under my spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.61,0:31:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother, don't be rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.09,0:31:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother! Third brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.02,0:31:45.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1255.128,623.742)}Dangyang\N Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.82,0:31:53.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}Elder brother could not be seen—
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.82,0:31:55.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}—even in such short distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.82,0:32:01.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,1016.902)}Why don't I raise the dust as a tactic to deceive the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.82,0:32:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,998.561)}Soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.40,0:32:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,1016.902)}Go cut down branches \Nand tie them to your horse's tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.55,0:32:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,1016.902)}Divide into two! One group run west to east!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.05,0:32:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,1016.902)}The other run east to west!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.55,0:32:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord16.303}{\pos(696.023,1016.902)}This will raise the dust and look like an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.58,0:32:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.80,0:32:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhang, where is the Lord now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.13,0:32:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Lord is now hiding in the woods over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.62,0:32:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you have any news about Zilong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:49.61,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(272.443,747.902)\fade(255,0,255,0,310,5900,6200)}Jian Yong\NStyled: Xianhe
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.27,0:32:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for General Zhao, I would have met a violent death.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao has gone back to look for the two Ladies and the young Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.22,0:32:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please inform the Lord immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.15,0:32:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You must go yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:32:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.30,0:33:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.34,0:33:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.94,0:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.31,0:33:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.64,0:33:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Older brother, where is our Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.31,0:33:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the woods before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister-in-law, you must be startled!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.05,0:33:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.43,0:33:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lady, now that you are with General Zhang—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.39,0:33:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will look for Lady Mi and Adou again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the sword, that's the Chancellor's {\i1}Blue Pommel Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Return me the legendary sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.19,0:35:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, please save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.93,0:35:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any of you seen Lady Mi and the young Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.24,0:35:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady has the infant, but can't walk because she is wounded in her leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.00,0:35:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She is sitting by the broken wall over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.08,0:35:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Head for the east, General Zhang is waiting at the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.45,0:35:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you General Zhao! Thank you for rescuing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.07,0:35:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.07,0:36:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, I have come late—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.64,0:36:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,—and let you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.85,0:36:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are here, Adou will live!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.89,0:36:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Have pity that his father has wandered half his life with only him as his flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.86,0:36:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that you can protect Adou.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.63,0:36:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can see his father again, I can die without regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.64,0:36:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zhao Yun's sin to allow my Lady to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.81,0:36:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take my horse, my Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.05,0:36:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight on foot beside you and ensure that we make it out alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.49,0:36:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That cannot happen, how can you go without a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.49,0:37:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will entrust Adou completely under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.03,0:37:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I am already heavily injured, there would be no regrets if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can take him ahead! I don't want to drag you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.41,0:37:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Mi, if I have found you but cannot protect you—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,—how can I look at my Lord in the face again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.55,0:37:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, quick! Go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.32,0:37:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Mi, please, the troops are near! Please mount the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.00,0:37:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I really cannot move and should not be a burden to both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.70,0:37:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady, please mount the horse now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.72,0:37:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Adou will be left in your care, General
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.76,0:38:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, quick! Go that way, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.80,0:38:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady, please mount the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.67,0:38:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.85,0:38:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady, please mount the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.15,0:38:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.99,0:38:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,General, there is someone here! Quick, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.12,0:39:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.59,0:39:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady, my Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady!
